247
00:29:11,599 --> 00:29:14,000
[SPEAKER_04] Da, to je to.

248
00:29:15,359 --> 00:29:16,799
[SPEAKER_04] Ne znam šta bi još drugo rekao o tome.

249
00:29:16,960 --> 00:29:17,759
[SPEAKER_05] Hajmo dalje onda.

250
00:29:18,960 --> 00:29:20,000
[SPEAKER_05] Jel ima Pjecak?

251
00:29:20,319 --> 00:29:21,039
[SPEAKER_05] Hajde bravo.

252
00:29:22,799 --> 00:29:24,880
[SPEAKER_04] Kako kaže grupa The Purple Child in Time.

253
00:29:29,039 --> 00:29:33,440
[SPEAKER_05] Kako ono, kad se spominje ovaj Mješokovača, odmah u glavi, ostala si uvijek.

254
00:29:34,160 --> 00:29:40,160
[SPEAKER_04] Pa to, zašto, čovjek je shvatio YouTube prije YouTube, shvatio da su ljudi došli zbog referenata.

255
00:29:40,319 --> 00:29:42,079
